General.Name: Propell Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Propell Holdings Limited operates a finance platform for small and medium enterprises in Australia. The company provides lending and payment solutions; insights for financial health; and direct access to a suite of finance tools. Propell Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
